\par 
\par "I'd like to know what that last-minute Security inspection of Ramsey was all about," said Garcia.
\par 
\par "Shut up!" barked Sparrow.  "Until there's proof positive to the contrary, he's one of us.  So are you and Les.  And so am I."  His mouth twisted in faint amusement.  "We're all in the same boat."  The lips thinned.  "And we've a bigger and more imme
diate problem."  He balanced a tube on the scales, replaced it.  "How can we break radio silence to notify home base of what we've discovered?"
