\par 
\par Ramsey straightened.  "That's a stupid order.  If something happened to you we couldn't go on."
\par 
\par "Are you suggesting I should confide our destination in you?"
\par 
\par Ramsey hesitated, thought:  I already know it.  What would happen if I indicated that to Sparrow?  That'd confirm his opinion that I'm Security.
\par 
